Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.21,0:01:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要从谁开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.76,0:01:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.07,0:01:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后觉得先从由依开始比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.38,0:01:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在大食堂游击演唱会上的那个乐队主唱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.90,0:01:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙总是特别活泼  以欺负日向为乐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.43,0:01:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还当上了乐队的主唱  做着自己喜欢的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.78,0:01:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她应该已经相当满足了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.59,0:02:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来只要我们从后面推她一把
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.59,0:02:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就能离开这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.84,0:02:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这样觉得的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话不是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.91,0:02:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你赞成吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.12,0:02:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  就这么定了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.15,0:02:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你准备得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛  虽然花了点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.10,0:02:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「handsonic  version5」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.92,0:02:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是handsonic  version5
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.28,0:02:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这哪像是天使  完全是个恶魔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你说冷酷的天使要更加邪恶  所以我才做成这样子的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.95,0:02:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  很好啊  很讨人厌的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.75,0:02:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨人厌…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.86,0:02:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  很好  真的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.51,0:02:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  还能长对翅膀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.84,0:02:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翅膀？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.08,0:02:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要翅膀干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢  看上去不是更帅一些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.24,0:02:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看上去更帅一些才好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:02:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样才更像天使啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:02:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.05,0:03:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你趁她在乐队练习时出现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.91,0:03:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「收到了其他社团对你们的噪音投诉」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.41,0:03:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后指着由依这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.77,0:03:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「尤其是你的吉他噪音特别大」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.31,0:03:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「因为你的缘故  乐队死了」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「因此我要暂时没收你的吉他」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后你就拿走由依的吉他  离开那里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话由依肯定会追上来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就逃  然后到院子里来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.42,0:03:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里我会假装冲出来撞到你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与此同时你就放开吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.27,0:03:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会接住吉他  你就顺势逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此创造出我和她单独相处的状况
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.86,0:03:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.17,0:03:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.19,0:03:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看准她练习的时候动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:03.15,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\pos(575,250)}教学楼A栋  空教室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:29.86,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Shine days
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  由依
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别用这种别扭的节奏唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.72,0:04:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由依  唱歌和弹奏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专心做好其中一样不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.10,0:04:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这样子下去实在太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.73,0:04:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能这样  岩泽前辈也是弹唱兼顾的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.54,0:04:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为岩泽在这两方面都很优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有在努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要求得太严格了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.18,0:04:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演唱会时又没冷场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.07,0:04:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这次可是新曲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的吉他  乐队死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就看穿了乐队现在的弱点？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.38,0:04:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不是普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.87,0:04:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也懂音乐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会  我还以为大家都没注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我要暂时没收你的吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.82,0:05:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  由依
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.78,0:05:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.05,0:05:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么只有你一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.95,0:05:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她没追上来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.04,0:05:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  没了吉他后不就好了很多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不觉得这样音域薄了很多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.54,0:05:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有主旋吉他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.39,0:05:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再加一个伴奏吉他算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.91,0:05:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想说的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乐队的主唱还是得背个吉他才能打动听众
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底懂不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.88,0:05:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇  这家伙对尚子发飙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:05:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去把吉他拿回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我站住  由依！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了  给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  抛太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.13,0:06:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.76,0:06:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  接住了的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是前辈救了它啊  从天使手里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.31,0:06:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙上哪去了  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  「混蛋」个头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做事还是那么随心所欲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随心所欲？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是都当上乐队的主唱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉他也弹了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点东西远远不够啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.48,0:06:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他还有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊  很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.28,0:06:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.17,0:06:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们先换个地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  还有其他什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.72,0:07:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不想说的话也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  说给你听
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.67,0:07:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊  想做的事情比一般人多得多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得这是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因是那个吧  活着的时候没能做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小时候  被车子从后面撞到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后身体就瘫痪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.76,0:07:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都卧床不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人照顾的话根本活不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都要依靠我的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得很对不起她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过电视还是能看的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:07:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着音乐节目里的乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心想要是自己也能那样该多好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那现在不是挺好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.76,0:08:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  还有什么事想做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还经常有看棒球转播
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棒球的话不是已经在球技大赛上打过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候没打出来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,触棒打？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本垒打
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.79,0:08:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不打出本垒打不算吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.74,0:08:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想等乐队那边熟练起来之后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.28,0:08:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也该好好练习下棒球了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.41,0:08:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要兼顾这两方面可是非常辛苦的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且再问一下  其他还有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.07,0:08:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足球？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很流行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…话是这么说没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也太多了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个世界的人能够同时兼顾乐队棒球还有足球的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说还有吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.35,0:08:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,职业摔跤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙  哪个世界的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…她憧憬的全是电视里看到的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要把她刚才说的都实现也未免太辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.01,0:09:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.76,0:09:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会帮你实现的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从方便的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就试试职业摔跤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,职业摔跤？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用什么招式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,German  suplex
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}德式拱桥摔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种夸张的招式怎么做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换成关节技之类能做到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.15,0:09:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很憧憬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,German  suplex
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.26,0:09:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且就那样着地获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么一副天真的样子说这么可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.77,0:09:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  那么来试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.78,0:09:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你比我想的要有力气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.93,0:09:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行能行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.19,0:09:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我这样的女孩子办不到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.38,0:10:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  差点就成功了啊  很可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.48,0:10:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那能再来一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先去下面有草的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死不掉的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.86,0:10:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这可不是在开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撑不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  下次一定会成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是最后一次了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊  该不会是连后桥都做不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然能了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.43,0:10:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就做做看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.46,0:10:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题果然是出在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为这个  我好几次差点失去意识都白费了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先从后桥的特训开始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别废话  快做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:11:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.31,0:11:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.86,0:11:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是从没有做过这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不会这个的话  German  suplex也没法做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.49,0:11:14.13,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(320,220)\fad(200,200)}数小时后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成…成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还抖个不停  不过算了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手臂依然牢牢地扣在腹部上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美  太完美了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,German  suplex！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1…2…3…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当当当  比赛结束
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.17,0:11:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做到了  我做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.91,0:11:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做到了  万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.49,0:12:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事究竟还要持续多久…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做到了  做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.40,0:12:22.48,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\pos(575,250)}教学楼  走廊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就足球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.82,0:12:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一对一单挑就可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.64,0:12:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  当然得是连过5人的带球射门
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马拉多纳哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这我知道的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  TK
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.37,0:12:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道松下五段在哪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.46,0:12:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的他不能像我这样跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.88,0:12:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't  let  me  cry
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然了  于是在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在山里  in  the  mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.17,0:12:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在山里？还真是个和练习跳舞完全没关系的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那暂时不会回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.27,0:13:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能帮忙把我说的人马上找来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:11.89,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\pos(575,250)}教学楼C栋  男厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.36,0:13:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对由理要保密
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使寄来了这样一封信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.26,0:13:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「一个女孩子都对付不了」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「还敢自称是男子汉吗  真是贻笑大方」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.05,0:13:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「贻笑大方」你竟然会读这个词
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.43,0:13:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋治好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  就算是笨蛋也会读哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.79,0:13:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「遵照运动员精神」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「让我来纠正你们那娘娘腔的性格」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.15,0:13:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「放学后在足球场等你们」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.18,0:13:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「天使」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内容真是莫名其妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是那家伙写的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.49,0:13:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的天使已经不是以前那个天使了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混杂了乱七八糟的东西才能写出这么傻的挑战书吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种蠢事我可不想奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.25,0:13:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去向游离子报告
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我说要对由理保密
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和由理说的话  又要演变成一场激烈的战斗了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  这里写着遵照运动员精神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.83,0:14:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是要堂堂正正以运动来决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.80,0:14:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这是写给我们男生的挑战书
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给由理打报告的话  不更显得我们没用了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就我们5人上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.41,0:14:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiss  you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就该这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:26.38,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\pos(575,250)}足球场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.65,0:14:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.64,0:14:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.85,0:14:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是由依吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.75,0:14:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在这里做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.53,0:14:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.48,0:14:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她开始踢球了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.92,0:14:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我上了  混球们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  写信的人是她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是看不惯平时没什么用的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才做出这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  保护好球门
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战斗不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们男生要胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:14:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:14:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小看我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:14:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I  kiss  you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向  你守门
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我闪开  这群呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  真是差劲的带球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满是破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  过了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.80,0:15:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么  野田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.16,0:15:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.76,0:15:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裁判  刚才那该给红牌的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全上垒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.41,0:15:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是从哪来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没结束呢  混球们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.31,0:15:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  TK  音无
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Easy  come  easy  go
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.77,0:15:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.67,0:15:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here  we...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.49,0:15:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是哪边的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.19,0:15:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算杀了你也要得分！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.33,0:15:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的运动员精神到底去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.52,0:15:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那玩意关我屁事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.30,0:15:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必杀  杀人断头台射门
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是想杀我还是想射门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吐槽点太多的射门朝我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.84,0:16:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇迹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.84,0:16:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.61,0:16:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.18,0:16:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.78,0:16:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连过5人完成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.40,0:16:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们竟然输了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手只有由依一个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.18,0:16:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高高升起  重重摔下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事一定要保密
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.12,0:16:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然球被抢断过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.45,0:16:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有过守门员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像场闹剧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.46,0:16:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那就开始下一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.63,0:16:55.73,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\pos(575,250)}棒球场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在开始前先问一下  把球打到哪里算是本垒打
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:16:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然是打到围栏的外面了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先尽力打打看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.44,0:17:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.47,0:17:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是打中了就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.23,0:17:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看准球  用球棒的中心部分来击球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击球点太偏上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.11,0:17:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次太偏下了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭着眼睛怎么可能打中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太没力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.14,0:17:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然在加油啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.42,0:17:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太累了  手的握力也下降了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天再继续下去也是徒劳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.59,0:18:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫的声音虽然很响  但击出的球完全不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.64,0:18:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天已经黑了  都看不清球了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.01,0:18:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.31,0:18:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.68,0:18:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要来吗  真正的棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全力挥棒么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.27,0:18:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近都没做过了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:18:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样或许也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.97,0:19:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  完全没碰到球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.54,0:19:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.02,0:19:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.90,0:19:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.49,0:19:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也难怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.99,0:19:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总归是办不到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经可以了  这个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.64,0:19:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别放弃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.02,0:19:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.73,0:19:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要为我做这些事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.78,0:19:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些是你曾想做的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.91,0:19:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要努力到最后啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本垒打什么的只是个开玩笑一般的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.48,0:19:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使没打出本垒打
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.37,0:20:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但让身体做了这么多的运动  所以已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.99,0:20:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都仿佛是在社团活动  太开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.34,0:20:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过吗  那时我的身体动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.17,0:20:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.42,0:20:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  已经全都实现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现？  实现什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.58,0:20:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体无法动弹时想做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.21,0:20:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.65,0:20:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女性究极的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.12,0:20:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我没法做家务  洗衣服也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说那些了  一个人的话什么都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.95,0:20:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一个光会给别人添麻烦的包袱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.33,0:20:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁会要我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.42,0:20:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神真是太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.62,0:20:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的幸福全都夺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.17,0:20:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么前辈  你会和我结婚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.11,0:21:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.61,0:21:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会和你结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.70,0:21:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的真心话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.06,0:21:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.54,0:21:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈根本不了解真正的我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.12,0:21:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现实中的  活着的你无论是什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都会和你结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.11,0:21:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你有什么残疾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.64,0:21:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由依无法走路  站都站不起来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.31,0:21:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说了不管你有什么残疾的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.09,0:21:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使无法走路  无法站立
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.43,0:21:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至无法生育
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.20,0:21:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此我也会和你结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.51,0:22:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一生都陪伴着你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.71,0:22:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里遇到的你  不是由依的替身
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.53,0:22:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真正的由依啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.26,0:22:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论在哪里遇到你  我都会喜欢上你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.19,0:22:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在六十亿分之一的概率下再次相遇的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.12,0:22:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使那时候你的身体依旧无法动弹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.93,0:22:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会和你结婚的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.31,0:22:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会相遇的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.08,0:22:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为由依一直躺在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.17,0:22:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是个打棒球的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.13,0:22:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某天把你家窗户给打碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.77,0:22:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我去捡球的时候看见了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.04,0:22:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我们的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.34,0:22:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聊了一会儿  发现我们非常合得来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.27,0:22:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉中我每天都会去你家了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.71,0:22:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也开始照顾你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.29,0:22:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的如何
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.51,0:22:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.22,0:23:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.99,0:23:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让一直以来都是一个人在照顾我的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.72,0:23:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻松一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.31,0:23:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.23,0:23:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.84,0:24:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.82,0:24:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.36,0:24:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以后打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.49,0:24:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会等到最后的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.34,0:24:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟还有那么多让人挂念的家伙留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.24,0:24:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.08,0:26:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚刚劈了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.58,0:26:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影子？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.67,0:26:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说清楚点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.74,0:26:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能说是影子
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.14,0:26:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被刚刚赶来的野田打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.47,0:26:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只有大山一个人的话就危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.74,0:26:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.03,0:26:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么危险
