Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.54,0:26:48.55,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,320)\fad(100,100)}又干了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.89,0:26:49.48,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(250,350)\fad(100,100)}他居然会被弄掉眼镜…
