Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.77,0:26:50.34,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(250,320)\fad(100,100)}我想救他的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.68,0:26:50.68,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,320)\fad(100,100)}我不需要帮忙！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.11,0:26:51.23,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(250,350)\fad(100,100)}太不正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.42,0:26:52.42,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(460,350)\fad(100,100)}有东西跑进来了  音无同学！
