Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.45,0:26:54.10,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(250,350)\fad(100,100)}还不如被天使消灭更好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.78,0:26:53.36,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,350)\fad(100,100)}会消失的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.74,0:26:54.52,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,320)\fad(100,100)}到底发生什么了
